STEP 4 — VERIFY STEPS ADDED
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
For each test issue, verify steps were added:

curl -s \
  -X POST \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer XRAY_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "query": "{ getTest(issueId: \"11108\") { steps { id action data result } } }"
  }' \
  https://xray.cloud.getxray.app/api/v2/graphql

